You are flexible, communicative and strongly oriented to customer service. You are driven by entrepreneurial spirit and love challenges. You are a good team player and have good organizational skills. You already demonstrated your critical thinking and logic as well as your analysis and synthesis skills;
Your mother tongue is (Swiss-) German or French and you are fluently bilingual in the other language. Knowledge of
English is an advantage;
